{"tid":2159160,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"巴郡、高盛、橋水、高瓴基金 第二季持倉公佈","createTime":"2020-08-16T07:00:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-17T01:56:34.000Z","uid":1086,"like":4,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"354fe07a8b4efdd6a9765526c61d5ad6dccce96d","tid":2159160,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T07:00:09.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\"><strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">巴郡</span></span></strong></p><br />\n巴郡前五大標的持倉不變！值得注意的是，一季度第五大持倉為富國銀行，遭遇減持後排名第7，卡夫亨氏晉升為二季度第五大持倉。<br />\n<img src=\"https://postimg.futunn.com/2020081500060015610652bae4b.png/logo\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpostimg.futunn.com%2F2020081500060015610652bae4b.png%2Flogo&h=b9764d97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在5月初的伯克希爾股東大會上，巴菲特稱未來顯得模糊不清，現在應當謹慎下注。<br />\n<br />\n今年連續兩個季度，我們都相當罕見地見到了伯克希爾較大規模的清倉行為。<br />\n<br />\n在5月初的年度股東大會上，巴菲特表示已經清倉所有航空股，包括西南航空、聯合大陸航空、達美航空、美國航空。值得注意的是，2月的時候巴菲特曾增持達美航空，稱疫情不影響判斷。<br />\n<br />\n二季度伯克希爾減持了11家公司，涉及金融、通信兩大板塊，其中8家公司屬於金融板塊。<br />\n<img src=\"https://postimg.futunn.com/202008150006000739972f99048.png/logo\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpostimg.futunn.com%2F202008150006000739972f99048.png%2Flogo&h=2741091c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMore:<br />\n<em>巴菲特二季度狂賺263億美元，現金儲備1466億美元！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2149663\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2149663</a></em><br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">高盛</span></span></strong></p><br />\n從持倉偏好來看，金融、IT類及醫療保健個股位列前三，佔總持倉的比例分別為29.04%，17.05%以及12.04%。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://postimg.futunn.com/20200813000596293a59fbfa80d.png/big\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpostimg.futunn.com%2F20200813000596293a59fbfa80d.png%2Fbig&h=408ec550&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">橋水</span></span></strong></p><br />\n<img src=\"https://postimg.futunn.com/20200813000595424793e0dd663.png/logo\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpostimg.futunn.com%2F20200813000595424793e0dd663.png%2Flogo&h=deeeecbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://postimg.futunn.com/20200813000595424793e0dd663.png/logo\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpostimg.futunn.com%2F20200813000595424793e0dd663.png%2Flogo&h=deeeecbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n橋水基金同時還持有大量新興市場ETF，前十大持倉資產中佔據3席，分別為新興市場ETF-Vanguard MSCI、中國大盤股ETF-iShares、中國ETF-iShares MSCI。<br />\n<br />\n雖然橋水基金在美股的持倉以投資指數ETF為主，但仍然對個股有不少配置。聚焦中概股來看，諸多中概股得到了大幅度的加倉，其中蔚來得到增持1028%，此外中通快遞、騰訊音樂、微博等知名中概股也得到不小的加倉。<br />\n但需要注意的是橋水基金對這些個股的投資金額較小。<br />\n<img src=\"https://postimg.futunn.com/20200813000595578782d409f68.png/big\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpostimg.futunn.com%2F20200813000595578782d409f68.png%2Fbig&h=3b86c648&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">高瓴</span></span></strong></p><br />\n高瓴資本在美股持有74家公司的股票，以生物醫療、互聯網科技為主要佈局領域，持有市值達到109.4億美元（760.34億元人民幣），截至2020年二季度末，在高瓴資本的美股持倉中，中概股佔據前十大重倉股中的八個席位。高瓴資本專注互聯網、醫藥、消費板塊，<ins>目前總管理資產650億美元，是亞洲規模最大、投資業績最好的私募基金管理人之一</ins>。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://postimg.futunn.com/202008150005999465c3a94d68d.png/logo\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpostimg.futunn.com%2F202008150005999465c3a94d68d.png%2Flogo&h=73f79ba3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n目前高瓴在生物醫藥、醫療器械、醫療服務、醫藥零售等領域累計投資了160多家企業，其中中國企業超過100家。總投資金額超過1200億元人民幣，投資企業總市值超過2.5萬億元。<br />\n<br />\n其中，在二季度，拼多多的漲幅超過138%，嗶哩嗶哩期內漲幅超過97%，百濟神州、京東等個股均大漲超過48%。<br />\n<br />\n高瓴依然看重中國企業對國家和世界經濟社會帶來的巨大改變，「重倉中國」的戰略也得到了深刻的展現。<br />\n<img src=\"https://postimg.futunn.com/202008150005999313c64a4f566.png/logo\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpostimg.futunn.com%2F202008150005999313c64a4f566.png%2Flogo&h=ba02fea9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<img src=\"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple114/v4/3a/39/c9/3a39c929-ce3a-1a7f-64d2-97df0e2c4e26/AppIcon-1x_U007emarketing-0-7-0-85-220.png/246x0w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fis1-ssl.mzstatic.com%2Fimage%2Fthumb%2FPurple114%2Fv4%2F3a%2F39%2Fc9%2F3a39c929-ce3a-1a7f-64d2-97df0e2c4e26%2FAppIcon-1x_U007emarketing-0-7-0-85-220.png%2F246x0w.png&h=2797287c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"56c7d7902fde83a59e073cf3d9d834961dd92c97","tid":2159160,"uid":340796,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T07:13:28.000Z","msg":"hillhouse 專買大陸野"},{"pid":"717a2d9bb549925aceb76527d7bc9fd8b7925c0c","tid":2159160,"uid":227698,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T07:13:28.000Z","msg":"橋水買NIO<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dd339ad389bf3de8da81e4e691f3257ae56372b","tid":2159160,"uid":91813,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"717a2d9bb549925aceb76527d7bc9fd8b7925c0c","tid":2159160,"uid":227698,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T07:13:28.000Z","msg":"橋水買NIO<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T07:14:50.000Z","msg":"間嘢出名廢<br />\n估唔到真係咁on9買中概股<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47c91cd559e66cdfd6e61db9eea7d683e7856c66","tid":2159160,"uid":340796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"56c7d7902fde83a59e073cf3d9d834961dd92c97","tid":2159160,"uid":340796,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T07:13:28.000Z","msg":"hillhouse 專買大陸野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T07:16:00.000Z","msg":"不過佢係私募基金黎<br />\n其他嗰啲係對沖"},{"pid":"37a0b0d37c365e062bdf64449a5d3c5788f5031b","tid":2159160,"uid":29836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T09:34:28.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"7b6b70db5b565ebf416a3b49137bd5a0d4933a30","tid":2159160,"uid":94824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-